2026-02-27 02:17:26.571 +01:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[@__userSourceIds_0='?' (Size = 79), @__userEmail_1='?' (Size = 27)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT "e0"."Key" AS "Date", COUNT(*) AS "Count"
FROM (
    SELECT rtrim(rtrim(strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%f', "e"."OccurredAt", 'start of day'), '0'), '.') AS "Key"
    FROM "Events" AS "e"
    WHERE "e"."SourceId" IN (
        SELECT "u"."value"
        FROM json_each(@__userSourceIds_0) AS "u"
    ) AND instr(lower("e"."RawPayload"), @__userEmail_1) > 0
) AS "e0"
